Vehement/Sun Crusher/Reflector/Unicron/Shockwave:




Vehement felt a surge of power that wasn't his own and he stood, only to be 
struck in the chest with two missiles, sending him slamming into the ground, 
his armor not that badly damaged but his energy reserves only at 45%.

---

Sun Crusher raised an arm, launching two grenades from the cannon attached to 
the arm's wrist at two incoming missiles.

---

Reflector lay on the ground, the missiles rocking his body as they hit.

===

Unicron blasted off through the air towards CF.
